Invocation Name: sophia's multiplication rush
des: Do you know more multiplication facts than your friends? Sophia's Multiplication Rush is a fun game created by Mrs. Burns's Third Grade to help kids learn their facts. Players have 10 seconds to name 5 things in a category. A judge then scores their responses. Grab some friends and family, and get ready to think fast. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint.
